<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA612_04_SU_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema612_04.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema612_04_su_0004">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y">각기둥의 구성 요소를 알아봅시다.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">각기둥에서 면과 면이 만나는 선분은 초록색으로, 선분과 선분이 만나는 점은 보라색으로 표시해 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="shape_box boolean_wrap">
            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA612_04_SU/0004_diagram_02.png" alt="육각기둥">

            <button data-answer-single="true" class="dot01"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="dot02"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="dot03"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="dot04"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="dot05"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="dot06"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="dot07"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="dot08"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="dot09"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="dot10"></button>

            <button data-answer-single="true" class="line01"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="line02"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="line03"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="line04"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="line05"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="line06 inline"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="line07"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="line08"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="line09"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="line10"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="line11 inline"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="line12 inline"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="line13"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="line14"></button>
            <button data-answer-single="true" class="line15"></button>
          </div> 
        </article>

        <article class="page page_2">
          <div class="flex_col_box">
            <div class="diagram_img">
              <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA612_04_SU/0004_diagram_05.png" alt="각기둥">
            </div>

            <div class="input_area">
              <h3 lang="y">두 밑면 사이의 거리를 어떻게 재면 좋을지 이야기해 보세요.</h3>

              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                <div class="example_box ex">
                  <p lang="y">옆면끼리 만나서 생긴 선분의 길이를 재면 될 것 같습니다.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_3">
          <div class="summarize_wrap">
            <div class="summarize">
              <label lang="y">약속해 볼까요</label>

              <div class="flex">
                <div class="diagram_set">
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA612_04_SU/0004_diagram_check_01.png" alt="오각기둥" class="img_d01">
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA612_04_SU/0004_diagram_check_02.png" alt="육각기둥" class="img_d02">

                  <p class="t01" lang="y">꼭짓점</p>
                  <p class="t02" lang="y">모서리</p>
                  <p class="t03" lang="y">높이</p>
                  <p class="t04" lang="y">높이</p>
                </div>

                <div class="sum_txt">
                  <div>
                    <span lang="y">각기둥에서 면과 면이 만나는 선분을</span><button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="1" lang="y">모서리</button><span lang="y">라 하고,</span>
                  </div>
    
                  <div>
                    <span lang="y">모서리와 모서리가 만나는 점을</span><button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="2" lang="y">꼭짓점</button><span lang="y">이라고 합니다.</span>
                  </div>

                  <div>
                    <span lang="y">또, 두 밑면 사이의 거리를</span><button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="3" lang="y">높이</button><span lang="y">라고 합니다.</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
